## 🧪 Verification Steps

1.  **Register/Login**: Sign in with an account.
2.  **Upload**: Select a `.mov` or `.mp4` file.
3.  **Process**: Watch the status bar move from **Upload** -> **Optimizing** -> **Published**.
4.  **Engage**: Like the video and leave a comment. Refresh the page to see them persist.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Action Required**: Please run the new [setup-engagement.sql](file:///C:/GOLive/setup-engagement.sql) in your Supabase SQL Editor to enable the likes and comments functionality on the live database.
